Constructor Detail

Decider

public Decider()
Notes: Things I would like taken care of for me: * all params in a hash (from both DB and ini file provided) * a list of hashmap that represent a filtered list of files by sample, study, experiment, workflow, etc * a list of files that represent the output from this workflow * a hash that joins the output of this workflow to their parents * the master list of results should be configurable, either to have all the processing events removed where this workflow has already been run or to include these
